PART A-RESEARCH QUESTIONS(SHORT ANSWERS)

Q1. Gemini 3.0 mein kya nayi improvements aayi?

ANS)Gemini 3.0 m new improvement y aayi hai wo wo phala sara models ka hisaab say bhout zaada fast or smart reasoning kerta hai,is ki contect window bhi bhout bari hai or y easily large files ko read kr ka samjh layta hai.multimodel (image+_audio+video)phala say zaada strong samajh layta hai y model.

Q2. Gemini 3.0 coding aur automation ko kaise improve karta hai?

ANS)Gemini 3.0 coding aur automation ko is tarha improve kerta hai wo gemini 3.0 ab AI agents se coding me madad deta hai, jo khud steps follow karte hain.vibe coding say sirf prompt likh kar puri app generate ho sakti hai.Terminal ke liye new bash automation tool bhi add kiya gaya hai.

Q3. Gemini 3.0 multimodal understanding ko kaise behtar banata hai?

ANS)Y Image,audio,video or documents ko detail m samjhta hai .Spatial reasoning(Dimag m 3D sochne ki ability e.g puzzle solve kerna) improve hui hai, matlab screens, layouts aur actions ko accurately samajhta hai.Video aur complex document reasoning stronger ho gayi hai.

Q4. Gemini 3.0 ke do developer tools ka naam likhen:

  1)Gemini CLI
  2)Antigravity developer platform
